#Structure

parentCat/:
1) the input catalogs for image simulation: star catalog, galaxy catalog, 
   observational information for each exposure ...
2) to store the output mock catalog

pype/:
the code to generate the simulated images.
1) defaultSim.param: parameter configuration file for the simulation
2) mockSample.py: routine to generate the mock catalog
3) chipSim.py:    routine to generate the image
4) imgMock.py, genStrFun.py: functions needed for the simulation

To generate the image, firstly run mockSample.py, then run chipSim.py

simg/:
to store the simulated images.

